323
# =========================================================================
# Ceeline Compact Dialect — Root Dictionary
# =========================================================================
# Format: Hunspell-compatible .dic
# First line: approximate stem count
#
# Each line: <stem>/<flags>
#   N = can take neg. prefix
#   R = can take re. prefix
#   P = can take prev. prefix
#   T = can take tent. prefix
#   D = can take del. prefix
#   Q = can take .seq suffix
#   O = can take .opt suffix
#   X = can take .ref suffix
#   A = can take .as alias suffix
#   M = can take .multi suffix
#   V = can take .v version suffix
#   C = can participate in compounds
#
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# HEADER — structural markers
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
@cl1
@cl2/V

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SURFACES — primary routing dimensions
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ho/NRPDQXMVC
dg/NRPQXVC
me/NRPDQXVC
rf/NRPQXVC
ts/NRPQXVC
rt/NRPDQXMVC
pc/NRPDQXVC
hs/NRPQXVC

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CHANNELS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
i/NTC
cu/NTC

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CONSTRAINT MODES
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
ro/NTDC
ad/NTDC
mu/NTDC

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# AUDIENCES
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
m/C
o/C
u/C

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
