# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SESSION VOCAB — placeholder for runtime additions
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Agents add stems here at runtime via vocab= clauses.
# All affix rules (N,R,P,T,D,Q,O,X,A,M,V) apply to vocab stems.
# Example: vocab=chk:checkpoint → chk/NRPQOXMVC

